      <li class="ctsh clearfix" data-cid="26317093">
        <div class="ilst">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/4334431/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u4334431-5.jpg" alt="浮躁" class="" /></a>
        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/26317093/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/26317093/" class="">第134页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/4334431/" class=" " title="浮躁">浮躁</a>
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="26317093">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">每一个人在他人的和外部强制下所习惯了的社会水准，最后将会在自我强制下顺利地复制。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2013-05-12 11:17</span>
                  
                    &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="">1人喜欢</span>
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                每一个人在他人的和外部强制下所习惯了的社会水准，最后将会在自我强制下顺利地复制。
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







